text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000413",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「だから何じゃ？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00102",
linknext="block_00104",
},
block_00104={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「草薙健一郎の遺産は俺が完成させる」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00103",
linknext="block_00105",
},
block_00105={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0004",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000414",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「ここまでの材料を集めたのは全部ワシじゃ。",
{"rt2"},
"後から出てきた分際でしゃしゃり出るな。ボケが」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00104",
linknext="block_00106",
},
block_00106={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「ああ、そうかもしれないな……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00105",
linknext="block_00107",
},
block_00107={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「だったら。俺は俺でやる。",
{"rt2"},
"俺を止めたかったら、無理矢理にでも止めてみるんだな。",
{"rt2"},
"ただし、俺はやると決めたら、絶対にやるがな」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00106",
linknext="block_00108",
},
block_00108={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0001",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000415",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00107",
linknext="block_00109",
},
block_00109={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0002",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000416",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「なんか立場がいつもと逆では無いか……。",
{"rt2"},
"なんだかだぞ草薙……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00108",
linknext="block_00110",
},
block_00110={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「まぁ、たしかにこういう台詞はお前にこそふさわしいよな」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00109",
linknext="block_00111",
},
block_00111={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0001",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000417",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「お前は一応はクール系でめんどくさそうにするキャラクターだと思われているのになぁ……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00110",
linknext="block_00112",
},
block_00112={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「そう思われている方が、面倒ごとがあちらから来なくて助かるがな」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00111",
linknext="block_00113",
},
block_00113={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1b0000",face="b0001",head="aka_z1b",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000418",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「自分からは首を突っ込むくせになぁ……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00112",
linknext="block_00114",
},
block_00114={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「そういう性分なんだよ。",
{"rt2"},
"だいたい巻き込まれた事件なんぞ、願い下げだが。",
{"rt2"},
"こちらから望んだトラブルなら大歓迎だ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00113",
linknext="block_00115",
},
block_00115={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「お前は、そういう俺の性格を良く分かってるのだろ？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00114",
linknext="block_00116",
},
block_00116={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1b0000",face="b0003",head="aka_z1b",lv=4,id=9},
{"fgact",ch="明石",act="うなづく",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000419",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「ふっ、退学ものなのじゃぞ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00115",
linknext="block_00117",
},
block_00117={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「そうかもなぁ……。",
{"rt2"},
"まぁ最低でも退学。下手したら警察につかまるレベルだろう。",
{"rt2"},
"たしか器物破損にあたるんじゃなかったか？　落書きって？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00116",
linknext="block_00118",
},
block_00118={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0001",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
delay={
vl01={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0003",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
},
},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000420",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「さぁな。良く分からんのぉ。",
{"rt2"},
"ただ、ワシはこの作品を完成させたいと思った。",
{"rt2"},
"ワシはこの作品を作る事によって、どんな罰でも受けようと思った」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00117",
linknext="block_00119",
},
block_00119={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0004",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
delay={
vl01={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0003",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
},
},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000421",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「芸術が反社会的なものであったとしても、罰せられる行為であったとしても――それが真に“美”であるなら、ワシはその美に殉じよう！",
{"rt2"},
"ワシはそう思ったのじゃ！」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00118",
linknext="block_00120",
},
block_00120={
{"mwact",act="びっくり"},
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「ぷっ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00119",
linknext="block_00121",
},
block_00121={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0009",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000422",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「何故笑うのじゃ！　今、そうとうワシはかっこよかったはずじゃぞ！」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00120",
linknext="block_00122",
},
block_00122={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「あ、いやぁな。お前らしからぬ……",
{"rt2"},
"いやある意味お前らしい大言壮語だと思ってな……笑えた」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00121",
linknext="block_00123",
},
block_00123={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0001",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000423",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「ワシじゃからな！　大言壮語も似合うじゃろ？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00122",
linknext="block_00124",
},
block_00124={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「どうでもいいが、一人で一晩で出来る作業か？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00123",
linknext="block_00125",
},
block_00125={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「俺が設計図をみたかぎりだと、一晩で作るのに一人では不可能。二人だってかなりつらい」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00124",
linknext="block_00126",
},
block_00126={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0003",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000424",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「まぁ、体力のある人間が数人は必要じゃろうな……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00125",
linknext="block_00127",
},
block_00127={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「やっぱり一人じゃ出来ないじゃねぇかよ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00126",
linknext="block_00128",
},
block_00128={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0000",face="a0002",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"fgact",ch="明石",act="ジャンプ",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000425",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「ばーか、凡人ならば不可能だと言っておるのじゃ。",
{"rt2"},
"凡人ならざるワシならば可能。",
{"rt2"},
"不可能を可能にするのがワシ、明石亘なのじゃ！」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00127",
linknext="block_00129",
},
block_00129={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「はぁ？　アホか。",
{"rt2"},
"出来るわけねーだろ……」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00128",
linknext="block_00130",
},
