{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000428",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「うるさい！　どこが貧相な体つきじゃ！",
{"rt2"},
"見よ！　この肉体美！」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00135",
linknext="block_00137",
},
block_00137={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「ガリガリじゃねーかよ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00136",
linknext="block_00138",
},
block_00138={
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000429",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「ソリッドな身体と言え！」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00137",
linknext="block_00139",
},
block_00139={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「んで？　そのソリッドな身体がどうしたんだよ？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00138",
linknext="block_00140",
},
block_00140={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0500",face="a0008",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
delay={
vl01={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0500",face="a0009",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
},
},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000430",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「草薙ぃぃ。ワシがコートを脱ぐ意味が分からんかぁ？",
{"rt2"},
"その恐ろしさがわからんのかぁ？",
{"rt2"},
"ああん？」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00139",
linknext="block_00141",
},
block_00141={
{"text"},
text={
ja={
{
name={"直哉"},
"「いいや」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00140",
linknext="block_00142",
},
block_00142={
{"fg",ch="明石",mode=3,path=":fg/aka/z1/",file="aka_z1a0500",face="a0003",head="aka_z1a",lv=4,id=9},
{"text"},
text={
vo={
{"vo",file="man_wtd_000431",ch="wtd"},
},
ja={
{
name={"明石"},
"「けっ、少しでも頭が切れる男と思ったワシがおろかじゃった。",
{"rt2"},
"所詮、貴様も凡夫の極みであったか、けっ、くそ虫がっ」",
{"rt2"},
},
},
},
linkback="block_00141",
linknext="block_00143",
},
block_00143={
{"se",id=1,file="se2192"},
{"fgact",ch="明石",act="うなづく",time=75,lv=4,id=9},
{"quake",mode="mw"},
